charges.charge_disposition: Deft committed to custody of BOP for 37 months. Special assess of $100. Supervised release for 4 years. Deft shall perform 200 hrs of community service as directed by probation, to be performed at a rate of not less than 100 hrg per year. At the time of referral to the program, he is to make payment of $150 payable to court community service to cover administrative costs. Fine of $6,920.00. (1)
